item.title: Office Hours
item.description: Welcome to the Automation Kit for Power Platform October 2022 office hours landing page. You can register for the office hours session https://aka.ms/ak4ppofficehours to be held on Tuesday 11th October 2022 between 7:00AM and 8:00AM PDT (See other times timezones https://aka.ms/ak4pp-times). If you have you already registered, you can forward this page or the registration link to others you feel may be interested.
